  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Describing a pharmacokinetic model of 48-h sevoflurane sedation in obese ICU patients
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Prospective clinical monocentric study in ICU with sedated ventilated obese patients with
      sevoflurane during 48 h with the AnaConda® system, establishing pharmacokinetic model of
      sévoflurane and its metabolites (hydroxyfluroisopropanol, fluoride)
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
